<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='641000' id='t-641000'>if you're watching a film or a book.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='644000' id='t-644000'>And I love those revolutions,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='647000' id='t-647000'>and I love the future that Milo brings.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:00
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='649000' id='t-649000'>Thank you very much indeed.</span>
</span>
</p>
